              </ul>
            </li>
            <li> <strong>Asset Mapping.</strong> A tool to help stakeholders examine assets and gaps within the maternal and child health system. Understanding assets will help stakeholders select priorities and act.
<ul>
            <li><a href="../documents/Needs-Assessment/Asset Mapping FINAL.docx">Scenario for using the tool</a></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Network Mapping and Analysis.</strong> A tool  to identify what partnerships and collaborations exist to support selected priorities. This tool helps identify linkages that need to be created or strengthened to reach our outcome.
<ul>
            <li><a href="http://media.sph.unc.edu/adobe/mch_ole/Workforce_Development/network_mapping/">Brief video overview of the tool</a></li>
                <li><a href="../documents/Needs-Assessment/Network Mapping and Analysis FINAL.docx">Scenario for using the tool</a></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
